	<h1 class="title">有病治病，研究者能“闻”出哪里出了问题</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/998/small/998.jpg?1402274915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐云路 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-10 14:06:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11934/medium/11934.jpg?1436635537" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


